import AboutUsCounter from '../../common/AboutUsCounter'

import HeroBanner3 from './HeroBanner3'

import RecentNewsPost3 from './RecentNewsPost3'
import SopnsorArea3 from './SopnsorArea3'
import Testimonial3 from './Testimonial3'
import UpCommingArea3 from './UpCommingArea3'

function HomePage3() {
  return (
    <>
     <HeroBanner3/>
     <CategoryArea3/> 
     <LiveAuction3/>
     <Testimonial3/>
     <UpCommingArea3/>
     <SopnsorArea3/>
     <RecentNewsPost3/>
     <AboutUsCounter/>
    </>

}

export default HomePage3
